# INSTRUCTIONS TO WRITE YOUR DOCKERFILE
# 1 The base image is UBuntu

# 2 run a get up
# 3 install python
# 4 install python package manager pip
# 5 Install flask using pip

# 6 copy the application to the /opt/ FOLDER in the image

# 7 make this your entrypoint  FLASK_APP=/opt/app.py flask run --host=0.0.0.0 --port=8080

